flowchart TD
    A[User opens system] --> B{Role}
    B -->|Student| C[Student Login or Google OAuth]
    B -->|Admin| D[Admin Login or Google OAuth]

    C --> E[Student Dashboard]
    D --> F{Admin Type}
    F -->|System Admin| G[System Admin Dashboard]
    F -->|Super Admin| H[Super Admin Dashboard]

    E --> I[Browse or Search Books]
    I --> J{Book available?}
    J -->|No| K[Show unavailable status]
    J -->|Yes| L[Create borrow request]

    L --> M{Approval required?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Create borrowing pending]
    M -->|No| O[Assign copy and create borrowing borrowed]

    N --> P[Notify admins]
    P --> Q[Admin reviews request]
    Q --> R{Approve?}
    R -->|No| S[Cancel request and notify student]
    R -->|Yes| O

    O --> T[Generate pickup QR and send claim email]
    T --> U[Student receives QR]
    U --> V[Admin scans pickup QR]
    V --> W{QR matches pending pickup?}
    W -->|No| X[Show mismatch warning]
    W -->|Yes| Y[Confirm pickup and set picked_up_at]

    Y --> Z[Borrow period active]
    Z --> AA{Due date reached?}
    AA -->|No| Z
    AA -->|Yes| AB[Mark overdue and send reminders]

    Z --> AC[Admin scans accession QR for return]
    AB --> AC
    AC --> AD{Active borrowing found?}
    AD -->|No| AE[Show no active borrowing]
    AD -->|Yes| AF[Confirm return]

    AF --> AG[Set return_date and returned status]
    AG --> AH[Increase available quantity]
    AH --> AI[Set copy status available]
    AI --> AJ[Create notifications and audit logs]

    G --> AK[Manage Books]
    H --> AK
    AK --> AL[Import CSV or XLSX]
    AL --> AM{ISBN exists?}
    AM -->|Yes| AN[Update existing book]
    AM -->|No| AO[Insert new book]
    AN --> AP[Ensure copy and accession coverage]
    AO --> AP

    G --> AQ[Manage Borrowings]
    H --> AQ
    G --> AR[Manage Users]
    H --> AR
    H --> AS[Manage Admins and Settings]

    AJ --> AT[In-app notifications]
    AT --> AU[Unread counters and deep links]
    AB --> AV[Overdue email scheduler]
    T --> AW[Borrow claim email sender]

    C --> AX[CSRF-protected API calls]
    D --> AX
    AX --> AY[Session and role validation]
    AY --> AZ[Database transactions]
